br />\n<br />\n<strong>特典</strong><br />\n<ins>下載版特典</ins>：Quick ball 12粒！<br />\n<ins>Double Pack特典</ins>：2組極巨結晶(用作極巨團體戰挑戰由基拉和心鱗寶)<br />\n<ins>Pokemon Center/店鋪特典</ins>:(自己睇)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pokemon.co.jp/ex/sword_shield/lineup/190708_02.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pokemon.co.jp%2Fex%2Fsword_shield%2Flineup%2F190708_02.html&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=08a672d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pokemon.co.jp/ex/sword_shield/lineup/190708_02.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>POKEMON SECRET CLUB</strong><br />\n預約game個陣會俾個code你開acc做member<br />\n做左member後就有得抽獎 11月14日前加入可以得到USUM閃稜鏡、LPLE大鉗蟹、劍盾衫<br />\n<a href=\"https://swshmembers.pokemon.co.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fswshmembers.pokemon.co.jp%2F&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=0062b1ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://swshmembers.pokemon.co.jp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>其他消息</strong><br />\n新雲端 Pok&eacute;mon Home 手機Apps 將於2020年推出，玩家可以把Pokemon Bank, Let's Go &amp; GO的精靈單向傳送到最新遊戲 Pokemon 劍盾當中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGyHxVR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGyHxVR.png&h=586ef74f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/KDEWCoh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKDEWCoh.jpg&h=8e03693f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">參考網站(USUM資訊)</span></strong></ins>：<br />\n培育入門<span style=\"color: red;\">(新手必睇)</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://tut1.hkgpkm.pw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftut1.hkgpkm.pw&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=65f2b356\" target=\"_blank\">http://tut1.hkgpkm.pw</a><br />\n<br />\n傷害計算<br />\n<a href=\"https://pokemon-trainer.net/sm/dmcs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpokemon-trainer.net%2Fsm%2Fdmcs%2F&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=1a40fff9\" target=\"_blank\">https://pokemon-trainer.net/sm/dmcs/</a> (日)<br />\n<a href=\"https://pokemonshowdown.com/damagecalc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpokemonshowdown.com%2Fdamagecalc%2F&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=f50b3311\" target=\"_blank\">https://pokemonshowdown.com/damagecalc/</a> (英)<br />\n<br />\n個體計算<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.serebii.net/games/iv-calcsm.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.serebii.net%2Fgames%2Fiv-calcsm.shtml&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=bc3e8a7d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.serebii.net/games/iv-calcsm.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n最大耐久指數計算<br />\n<a href=\"http://pkc.client.jp/w/defmax.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpkc.client.jp%2Fw%2Fdefmax.html&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=fd01d25e\" target=\"_blank\">http://pkc.client.jp/w/defmax.html</a> (日)<br />\n<br />\n圖鑑/資料網站<br />\n<a href=\"http://serebii.net/pokedex-sm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fserebii.net%2Fpokedex-sm%2F&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=e3e4e841\" target=\"_blank\">http://serebii.net/pokedex-sm/</a> (英)<br />\n<a href=\"http://bokevon.web.fc2.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbokevon.web.fc2.com%2F&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRW58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=9af99116\" target=\"_blank\">http://bokevon.web.fc2.com/</a> (英日中)"},{"pid":"fc2370a2c3c9c195f8b3e811b7a0005409b1daaa","tid":1766582,"uid":177215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"我都開咗 自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90b74c41780faf23d24945b1feb27f713c6fae1","tid":1766582,"uid":177215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc2370a2c3c9c195f8b3e811b7a0005409b1daaa","tid":1766582,"uid":177215,"like":0,"dislik